The paper deals with secure network coding, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). It also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and security protocols (cs.SI), as well as coding theory (cs.CC). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
